cs.CG, cs.DS, cs.NA, cs.GR, cs.SC 

This paper deals with the problem of space-filling curves for nonconforming adaptive meshes, which is a topic related to computational geometry (cs.CG) and data structures (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the use of the curve for numerical analysis (cs.NA) and graphics (cs.GR), as well as its potential applications in scientific computing (cs.SC).
